Grammy award winner, Wizkid has posted his Grammy award plaque on his Instagram stories, weeks after his colleague Burna Boy posted his. The singers won the Grammys in different categories at the just- concluded award ceremony. On March 14, 2021, Big Wiz won ‘Best Music Video’ for his role on ‘Brown Skin Girl’ at the 63rd Grammy Award. He won the award alongside Beyonce, who owns the song and featured artists Saint Jhn and Blue Ivy. The award will also go to Jenn Nkiru who directed the video. The song was made for Beyonce’s album, Lion King: The Gift which featured other Nigerian artists.